stuck)\nSystem: • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\nSystem: • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\nSystem: • Blockers: ⚠️ Stuck Telegram delivery cron | ⚠️ DTLX subagent failures (model/provider errors, persistent baseline)\nSystem: \nSystem: — Orbis 🌐\nSystem: [2026-04-14 10:58:18 UTC] 🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 10:56 UTC 14 Apr\nSystem: \nSystem: Changes detected:\nSystem: • QLHV group (-5163901258) — **RECOVERED** — session re-spawned ~10:49 UTC, back running ✅\nSystem: • ⚠️ cron:ac986a8d — still stuck since ~10:04 UTC (~52 min), retrying Telegram delivery\nSystem: \nSystem: Pipeline: **DEGRADED** ⚠️ (persistent baseline, no new failures)\nSystem: • Active sessions: 4\nSystem: • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\nSystem: • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\nSystem: • Blockers: ⚠️ Stuck Telegram delivery retry cron (~52 min) | ⚠️ DTLX subagent failures (model/provider errors — pre-existing)\nSystem: \nSystem: — Orbis 🌐\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:01:25 UTC] 🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | 10:59 UTC 14 Apr\nSystem: \nSystem: Changes detected:\nSystem: • cron:e7885813 (Agent Status) — now running (~10:43 UTC activity), previously captured as done at 10:56 UTC. May have restarted. No new failures detected.\nSystem: • ⚠️ cron:ac986a8d (Telegram delivery retry) — still stuck ~55 min, retrying. Telegram gateway delivery remains unreliable.\nSystem: \nSystem: Pipeline: **DEGRADED** ⚠️\nSystem: • Active sessions: 4\nSystem: • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\nSystem: • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\nSystem: • Blockers: ⚠️ Stuck Telegram delivery retry cron (~55 min) | ⚠️ DTLX subagent failures (model/provider errors — pre-existing baseline, no new failures)\nSystem: \nSystem: — Orbis 🌐\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:03:47 UTC] State updated. No report sent — pipeline stable since last 10:59 UTC delivery.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:05:04 UTC] Comparing current session state against heartbeat state (11:01 UTC).\nSystem: \nSystem: **Changes detected since last report (10:59 UTC):**\nSystem: - `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492` session is now **done** (ended ~10:55 UTC — completed DTLX BE status report to Lead)\nSystem: - All other sessions: stable, same statuses as last heartbeat\nSystem: \nSystem: No new failures. Pre-existing baseline unchanged. Pipeline stable.\nSystem: \nSystem: **Silent — updating state and exiting.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:07:56 UTC] Heartbeat state updated. No report sent — pipeline stable since last 10:59 UTC delivery.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:09:56 UTC] Heartbeat state updated (11:09 UTC). No changes detected — silent exit.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:12:49 UTC] Heartbeat state updated (11:12 UTC). No changes detected — silent exit.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:14:50 UTC] State updated (11:14 UTC). **Silent — no report sent.** Pipeline now shows healthy (Telegram retry cron resolved, no longer in sessions). All sessions stable since last check.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 11:15 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 11:15 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776165332744,"__openclaw":{"id":"2967b1b3","seq":102}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Quick check of sessions, no active non-cron sessions. Night silence doesn't apply yet. Pipeline healthy."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1784,"output":30,"totalTokens":58513,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":56699,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776165332908,"responseId":"062d54d6ffe475ecdb9227ad3daa3f6c","__openclaw":{"id":"086e2ad1","seq":103}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group